	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Also loved Mapper 68 (Sunsoft Mapper #4). Very simple, precise information, mirroring selection... VROM chunks are a little bigger, but I could live with that.
<br />Firebug's document on NES mappers has a lot of holes in it. Most of the mappers don't have precise information on the mirroring selection registers... that makes it difficult to pick an appropriate mapper.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
